products.title: Unilux PVC Blackout Flamingo Pink Roller Blind
products.description: Embrace fantastic flamingo pink & give your bathroom or kitchen a modern makeover with the unilux pvc blackout roller blind. This roller blind is made from moisture resistant pvc and is guaranteed to give your space a fresh feel thanks to its contemporary design and crisp white finish. In addition, the blackout material will provide the required peace and privacy. Product id: sdb-rbx2380 fabric colour: flamingo pink material: fiberglass core laminated with pvc layered coating lining: colour match backing - see sample headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er3 - highest energy saving value - uv protection and effective thermal retention blackout: yes unilux pvc blackout flamingo pink roller blind in pink.
